### ✅ PAYMENT THROUGHPUT TEST REQUESTS
### File này có thể dùng với REST Client extension trong VS Code
### Hoặc copy vào Postman/Thunder Client

### 1. Test Payment Throughput (1000 payments)
POST http://localhost:8006/v1/test/payment/throughput
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalPayments": 1000,
  "batchSize": 100,
  "amount": 100000
}

###

